## Отладка

### Логирование

```python
from core.logging import get_logger

logger = get_logger(__name__)

@tool(name="debug", description="Debug tool", tags=["debug"])
async def debug_tool(param: str) -> str:
    logger.info(f"debug_tool called with param={param}")
    result = process(param)
    logger.info(f"debug_tool result={result}")
    return result
```

### Проверка mock режима

```python
import os

def is_test_mode() -> bool:
    return os.environ.get("TESTING", "").lower() in ("true", "1", "yes")

@tool(name="check", description="Проверка", tags=["debug"])
async def check_mode() -> str:
    if is_test_mode():
        return "Test mode"
    return "Production mode"
```

